00:01:57.730 --> 00:02:01.140
Today's program is titled
Making Patriotic Prostitutes:

00:02:01.140 --> 00:02:03.720
The South Korean Government's
Policies

00:02:03.720 --> 00:02:06.010 position:56%
on Prostitution for the US Military.

00:02:06.010 --> 00:02:10.370
It features scholar Jeong-Mi
Park, currently a Kluge fellow

00:02:10.370 --> 00:02:12.330
at the John W. Kluge Center.

00:02:12.330 --> 00:02:16.180
Dr. Park's research at the library
examines how the South Korean

00:02:16.180 --> 00:02:19.010
government controlled
military prostitutes catering

00:02:19.010 --> 00:02:23.090
to American servicemen in the
context of US military occupation,

00:02:23.090 --> 00:02:27.490
the hot and cold wars, economic
development and globalization.

00:02:27.490 --> 00:02:31.280
She also reveals the ways in
which the Korean government strove

00:02:31.280 --> 00:02:36.620
to make these "dangerous"
women into "patriotic subjects"

00:02:36.620 --> 00:02:39.990
who could contribute
to national security.

00:02:39.990 --> 00:02:45.140
Jeong-Mi Park earned her BA, MA and
PhD at the Department of Sociology,

00:02:45.140 --> 00:02:47.320
Seoul National University.

00:02:47.320 --> 00:02:51.560
She worked as a research assistant
professor at Hanyang University

00:02:51.560 --> 00:02:53.520
as a historical sociologist.

00:02:53.520 --> 00:02:57.480
She has analyzed the historical
transformations of state policies,

00:02:57.480 --> 00:03:00.920
citizenship and social
movements in South Korea

00:03:00.920 --> 00:03:03.910
from a perspective of
gender and sexuality.

00:03:03.910 --> 00:03:08.740
The title of her PhD dissertation
is A Study on Prostitution Policies

00:03:08.740 --> 00:03:12.920
in Korea: The Transformation of
the Toleration Regulation Regime

00:03:12.920 --> 00:03:18.130
and the Historical Constitution
of the Prostitute, 1945-2005.

00:03:18.130 --> 00:03:22.230 position:56%
She has published several papers in
Women's Studies International Forum,

00:03:22.230 --> 00:03:25.730
Korean Journal of Sociology
and Society and History.

00:03:25.730 --> 00:03:28.270
And most recently she has
