00:40:07.610 --> 00:40:10.500
that the government
prohibits prostitution

00:40:10.500 --> 00:40:14.360
but at the same time
forcibly examines prostitutes

00:40:14.360 --> 00:40:17.900
and prevents those with
STD's from working?

00:40:17.900 --> 00:40:22.310
