detained at a police station

00:40:22.310 --> 00:40:25.590
and subjected to some retrial.

00:40:25.590 --> 00:40:30.660 position:56%
Women who contracted gonorrhea or
other diseases were immediately sent

00:40:30.660 --> 00:40:35.980
to a detention center, usually a
village surrounded by mountains.

00:40:35.980 --> 00:40:38.490
